OL,7,F"Branches first brought resolutions
OL,8,Fregarding a lack of confidence in the
OL,9,Fsenior leadership team back in 2023
OL,10,Fdue to a number of issues relating to
OL,11,Fcrewing, shift patterns, reliance on
OL,12,Fovertime, training, IT and
OL,13,Foccupational health.
OL,15,F"Fire Brigades Union representatives
OL,16,Fhave worked closely with the Service
OL,17,Fover the last 6 months to seek
OL,18,Fimprovements to the issues raised.
